Wearing both wand and orb: damage-over-time abilities generate 1 Essence Corruption stack with each hit.
Essence Corruption:
Maximum stacks: 100
1 stack: damage-over-time abilities have a 30% chance to empower, dealing their damage instantly and refreshing their cooldown.
25 stacks: deal additional bonus damage with all attacks: extra damage is the sum of your magic level and the number of Essence Corruption stacks you have (thus a maximum of +199 damage).
50 stacks: basic abilities generate 3.6% additional adrenaline over 6 seconds.
Essence Corruption stacks do not expire, and are only removed when unequipping the corruption wand or orb.
